- name: managing services on target machine
  hosts: server1
  tasks:
    - name: installing apache2 server
      apt:
        name: apache2
        state: present
    - name: "starting apache2 server"
      service:
        name: apache2
        state: started
    - name: copy index.html file from control machine to target machine
      copy: src=index.html dest=/var/www/html/index.html mode=644



Output
First task installs apache server
second one is starting apache server
third one is copying a customized index.html file to the default directory of apache
